name: Leek & Associates
description: Firm proud to serve your financial needs
overview:
Stephen Leek founded the accounting firm that bears his name, Leek & Associates, in 1987. In addition to accounting services, the financial professionals at the firm also offer auditing, consulting and tax services. The accounting practice also serves as an informational resource to members throughout the community. The firm provides accounting services to individual clients as well as businesses and non-profit organizations.

Whether a small sole proprietor or a large corporation, the accountants at Leek and Associates possess the expertise to meet clients’ myriad needs. These financial professionals focus on helping all clients recognize and achieve their goals.
